<div class="wrapper wrapper-medium">
    <form action="destroy" class="form" disabled="disabled">
        <div class="field">
            <h2>We're sad to see you leave...</h2>
            <p>If we haven't said it lately, thanks for being a part of our community. We're always looking for new feature ideas and feedback, so don't be afraid to <a href="/contact">get in touch</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
            <label>To confirm, enter the domain for this site.</label>
            <input type="text" name="domain" placeholder="{{domain}}" autocomplete="off" autofocus="on">
        </div>

        <div class="field">
            <button type="submit" class="button secondary">Destroy This Site</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
